## 9. Final Summary

- **Overall Health Assessment**: **Excellent (Green)**
  The core of the ERP system is built on exceptional engineering practices. The foundation is highly responsive, utilizing modern components and standard security wrappers. The leave-proxy flow, timetable, and registration systems are premium-grade implementations.
- **Biggest Strengths**:
  1. High-fidelity UI styling built with HeroUI v3 and Tailwind CSS v4.
  2. Impeccable role-based routing and permissions middleware (`requirePermission`).
  3. Feature-complete Leave & Proxy management with automatic free-slot lookups.
- **Biggest Missing Areas**:
  1. Complete absence of Examination Seating and Eligibility appeals.
  2. Complete absence of Secure Examination Paper Generation (OTP and S3 encryption).
  3. Inactive Audit Logs system (schema exists but no logic writes to it).
- **Estimated Remaining Workload**: **~4 to 6 Weeks** of dedicated development to reach full Production Candidate status.
